قائمة الطعام في هذا المطعم تضم مجموعة واسعة من الخرفان الفاخرة، بدءًا من الحري الطازج المحلي من مزارعنا، وصولاً إلى الدواجن الرفيعة المذاق. يتم اختيار اللحوم بعناية فائقة لضمان الجودة العالية والنكهة المميزة.

name: Rasoi by Vineet
description:
Prepare for colour and culinary innovation at Rasoi by Vineet, our fine dining Indian restaurant operated by the first Indian Michelin-star chef, Vineet Bhatia. Rasoi means 'kitchen' in Hindi and here you will get to taste many signature dishes like the Tandoori lamb chop, Zataar-olive chicken tikka, butter chicken, lamb biryani and Kaffir lime prawns alongside the ever-popular samosa chaat.

Originally from Mumbai, Vineet Bhatia moved to London where he blazed a trail across the culinary world, re-thinking Indian food. He earned his Michelin Star for the first time in 2001. Discover his food art right here in Jeddah, for lunch or dinner.
